Context: To check if you require an English or Math Placement Assessment, students should refer to the Admissions Application Summary tab on their STU VIEW account. The following programs require a Math Placement Assessment: School of Management, School of Human Resources, School of Marketing, and General Arts and Science (R). Programs that do not require a placement assessment are not specified in the text. For more information, contact George Brown College at 416-415-2000 or TTY: 1-877-515-5559, or send an email to ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college's social media hub can also be visited for further details. Please note that the information on this website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered as a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
